	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><img src="http://www.seyken.com/download/igg/crystal-kingdom_poster_v4_3_opt.gif" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Do you remember the good old days when you sat in front of a TV and had to plug in a game cartridge in order to start up your favorite fantasy RPG? We remember those times, and that's why we started a fangame-based project called SEYKEN a few years back to celebrate them. It had online capability right from the start, and so we learned that there are quite a few people out there wanting the same. Now we'd like to take it one step further by creating our own original game, by fans for fans -- and you can become a part of it!<br /><br />Got your interest? <br /><br />Visit our Indiegogo Funding Campaign<br /><a href="http://www.indiegogo.com/seyken" class="postlink">Crystal Kingdom</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
